quran[70]{c,v,t}:
  26,111,"Iwo adati, “Kodi ife tikukhulupirire iwe pamene anthu onyozeka ndiwo amene amakutsatira iwe?”"
  26,112,"Nowa adati, “Kodi ine ndikudziwa chiyani za chimene iwo amachita?”"
  26,113,“Ambuye wanga ndiye amene akhoza kuweruza ngati mumazindikira.”
  26,114,“Ndipo ine sindidzathamangitsa anthu okhulupirira moona.”
  26,115,“Ine ndine wopereka chenjezo poyera.”
  26,116,"Iwo adati, “Iwe Nowa; ngati siusiya zimene uchita udzaponyedwa miyala.”"
  26,117,"Iye adati, “Ambuye wanga! Ndithudi anthu anga akundikana.”"
  26,118,Motero weruzani mwachilungamo pakati pa ine ndi iwo. Ndipulumutseni ine pamodzi ndi anthu okhulupirira amene ali ndi ine
  26,119,Ife tidamupulumutsa iye pamodzi ndi iwo amene adali naye m’chombo
  26,120,Ndipo pambuyo pake tidamiza ena onse ndi chigumula
  26,121,Ndithudi mu chimenechi muli phunziro komabe ambiri sakhulupirira
  26,122,Ndithudi Ambuye wako ndi Mwini mphamvu ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha
  26,123,Anthu a ku Aad sanakhulupirire Atumwi awo
  26,124,"Pamene m’bale wawo Houd adati, “Kodi inu simungakhale ndi mantha ndi Mulungu?”"
  26,125,“Ndithudi ine ndine Mtumwi wanu wokhulupirika.”
  26,126,“opani Mulungu ndipo munditsate ine.”
  26,127,"“Pa ntchito iyi, ine sindipempha malipiro kuchokera kwa inu chifukwa palibe wina amene angandilipire kupatula Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse.”"
  26,128,“Kodi inu mukumamanga nyumba pamalo paliponse pokwera mofuna kudzisangalatsa?”
  26,129,“Kodi muli kumanga nyumba zokongola ndi zolimba ngati kuti mudzakhalamo mpaka kalekale?”
  26,130,“Ndipo pamene mumenya anthu mumamenya ngati anthu ankhanza.”
  26,131,"“Motero opani Mulungu, ndipo mundimvere ine.”"
  26,132,“Ndipo muopeni Iye amene wakupatsani inu zinthu zonse zimene mumazidziwa.”
  26,133,"“Iye wakupatsani nyama ndi ana,”"
  26,134,“Ndiponso minda ndi a kasupe;”
  26,135,“Ndithudi ine ndili kuchita mantha ndi chilango chimene chidzadza pa inu pa tsiku loopsa.”
  26,136,"Iwo adati, “Ndi chimodzimodzi kwa ife kaya utilalikira kapena ayi.”"
  26,137,“Zonse zimene uli kutiopseza nazo ndi chikhalidwe cha anthu amakedzana.”
  26,138,“Ife sitidzalangidwa ayi.”
  26,139,Iwo adamukana iye ndipo Ife tidawaononga onse. Ndithudi mu chimenechi muli phunziro koma ambiri sakhulupirira ayi
  26,140,Ndithudi Ambuye wako ndiye Mwini mphamvu zonse ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha
  26,141,Anthu a Thamoud adakana Atumwi awo
  26,142,"Pamene m’bale wawo Saleh adati, “Kodi inu simungakhale ndi mantha ndi Mulungu?”"
  26,143,“Ndithudi ine ndine Mtumwi wanu okhulupirika.”
  26,144,“Motero opani Mulungu ndipo mundimvere ine.”
  26,145,“Pa ntchito iyi ine sindili kukupemphani malipiro. Palibe wina amene angandilipire kupatula Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse.”
  26,146,“Kodi inu muganiza kuti mudzasiyidwa mu mtendere wa m’dziko lino?”
  26,147,“M’kati mwa minda ndi a kasupe.”
  26,148,“Minda ya chimanga ndi mitengo ya tende imene yapatsa zipatso zambiri.”
  26,149,“Ndipo muboola mapiri ndi kumangamo nyumba zanu mwaukatswiri;”
  26,150,“Khalani ndi mantha ndi Mulungu ndipo mundimvere ine.”
  26,151,“Musamvere malamulo a anthu oononga.”
  26,152,“Amene amachita zoipa padziko lapansi ndipo sakonza makhalidwe awo.”
  26,153,"Iwo adati, “Iwe uli mmodzi mwa olodzedwa.”"
  26,154,“Iwe ndiwe munthu wonga ife tomwe. Tilangize chizindikiro ngati zimene ukunenazi ndi zoona”
  26,155,"Iye adati, “Iyi ndi ngamira yaikazi. Iyo idzamwa madzi patsiku lake ndipo inu mudzamwa patsiku lanu lokhazikitsidwa.”"
  26,156,“Musaizunze ayi chifukwa mukatero chilango cha tsiku loopsa chidzadza kwa inu.”
  26,157,Komabe iwo adaipha iyo ndipo adanong’oneza bombono
  26,158,Chilango chidawapeza iwo. Ndithudi mu chimenechi muli chizindikiro koma ambiri a iwo sakhulupirira
  26,159,Ndithudi Ambuye wako! Indedi ndiye Mwini mphamvu zonse ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha
  26,160,Anthu a Loti adakana Atumwi awo
  26,161,"Pamene m’bale wawo Loti adati, “Kodi inu simungaope Mulungu?”"
  26,162,“Ndithudi ine ndine Mtumwi wanu wokhulupirika.”
  26,163,“Opani Mulungu ndipo mundimvere ine.”
  26,164,“Ine sindili kupempha kuti mundilipire chifukwa cha ichi ayi chifukwa palibe wina amene angandilipire kupatula Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse.”
  26,165,“Kodi inu mwasankha kuti muzigonana ndi amuna anzanu mwa zolengedwa zonse
  26,166,“Kusiya akazi amene Mulungu adakulengerani? Koma inu ndinu anthu olakwa kwambiri.”
  26,167,"Iwo adati, “Iwe Loti! Ngati siusiya zimenezi ndithudi udzakhala mmodzi mwa othamangitsidwa.”"
  26,168,"Iye adati, “Ine ndili kudana ndi makhalidwe anu.”"
  26,169,“Ambuye wanga! Ndipulumutseni ine pamodzi ndi a pabanja langa ku ntchito zawo zoipa.”
  26,170,Ndipo Ife tidamupulumutsa iye pamodzi ndi anthu ake onse
  26,171,"Kupatula mayi wokalamba, pakati pa amene adatsalira m’mbuyo"
  26,172,Ndipo Ife tidawaononga kwambiri ena onse
  26,173,Ndipo choipa chidali chilango cha mvula imene idagwa pa iwo amene adachenjezedwa koma sadamvere
  26,174,Ndithudi mu ichi muli phunziro koma ambiri a iwo sakhulupirira
  26,175,Ndithudi Ambuye wako ndiye mwini mphamvu zonse ndi mwini chisoni chosatha
  26,176,Nawonso anthu okhala m’nkhalango adakana Atumwi
  26,177,"Pamene Shaibu adawauza kuti, “Kodi inu simungaope Mulungu?”"
  26,178,“Ndithudi ine ndine Mtumwi wanu wokhulupirira.”
  26,179,“Opani Mulungu ndipo mundimvere ine.”
  26,180,“Ine sindikupemphani malipiro chifukwa palibe wina aliyense amene angandilipire kupatula Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse.”